iencing 'Error 9001 (HY000): PD server timeout: start timestamp may fall behind safe point' with 431+ occurrences, causing HTTP 500 errors in frontend service. This indicates a database-level issue with the Placement Driver (PD) server in the distributed database system used by productcatalogservice.\",\n  \"next_verification\": {\n    \"action\": \"check_database_status\",\n    \"reason\": \"PD server timeout errors indicate database infrastructure issues\",\n    \"suggested_metrics\": [\"pd_server_uptime\", \"tidb_safe_point_lag\", \"database_connection_pool\"],\n    \"suggested_log_keywords\": [\"PD server\", \"safe point\", \"timestamp\", \"productcatalogservice\"]\n  }\n}\n```"}
